text: "F with U" is a song by American hip hop recording artist Kid Ink. The song was released on April 7, 2017 by Tha Alumni Music Group, 88 Classic and RCA Records, as the lead single from his EP 7 Series (2017). The track was produced by frequent collaborators DJ Mustard and J Holt, along with Hitmaka and vocals by Ty Dolla Sign. The song interpolates Tamia's "So Into You" as its chorus. ==Music video== The music video was released May 4, 2017.
